For the capital of Aram belongs to the {\scaps Lord},
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
as the tribes of Israel do,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}and also Hamath which borders on it.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Tyre and Sidon, for all their wisdom.
\par}

