\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and gold like the dirt of the streets.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}But now the Lord will dispossess her,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
