\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Ashkelon will remain uninhabited.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}A foreign people will settle in Ashdod,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and I will humble the pride of the Philistines.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}I will take their blood from their mouth,
