They also will be a remnant for our God,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
like a clan in Judah,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and Ekron will be like the Jebusites.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}But I will encamp as a guard about my house,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
