\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}Rejoice greatly, daughter of Zion!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Shout aloud, daughter of Jerusalem!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Look, your king comes to you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Vindicated and victorious is he,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
humble, and riding on a donkey,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
on a colt, the foal of a donkey.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}He will cut off chariots from Ephraim,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
