{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
from the river to the ends of the earth.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}And you, too \uc1\u8211* because of your blood covenant,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I have set free your prisoners from the waterless pit.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}To the stronghold will the prisoners of hope return.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
This day I declare, I will restore double to you.
