{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and travel on the whirlwinds of the south.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}The {\scaps Lord} of hosts will defend them.
\par}

