{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
like the crevices of the altar.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}And the {\scaps Lord} their God will save them on that day,
