\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
{\cf1\f1\fs22 12}An oracle. This is the message of the {\scaps Lord} about Israel. The {\scaps Lord} who stretches out the heavens, and lays the foundation of the earth, and forms the human spirit within people says:
\par}

