\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Look! I am about to make Jerusalem
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
a cup of drunkenness for all the surrounding peoples.
\par}

