There will be a siege of Jerusalem.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}On that day that I will make Jerusalem
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
