\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
But over the house of Judah I will keep watch,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
though I strike every horse belonging to the peoples with blindness.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}And the chieftains of Judah will say to themselves,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8220*The strength of the inhabitants is in the {\scaps Lord} of hosts their God.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}In that day I will make the chieftains of Judah
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
like a pan of fire in the woods,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
like a torch among sheaves,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
they will devour right and left all the surrounding peoples.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
