\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}And the {\scaps Lord} will first give victory to the tents of Judah,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
so that the glory of the house of David, and of the inhabitants of Jerusalem be not exalted above Judah.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}In that day the {\scaps Lord} will protect the inhabitants of Jerusalem,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and the feeblest among them will in that day be like David,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and the house of David like God, like the messenger of the {\scaps Lord} before them.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}And in that day I will seek to destroy all the nations who have come up against Jerusalem.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}And I will pour out on the house of David and the inhabitants of Jerusalem
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
the spirit of pity and compassion. They will look on him whom they have pierced
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and they will lament for him as one laments for an only son.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
They will bitterly grieve for him as one grieves for the firstborn.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}In that day mourning will be as great in Jerusalem
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
as the mourning for Hadad-rimmon in the plain of Megiddo.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}And the land will mourn, each family by itself:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
the family of the house of David by itself,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and their wives by themselves,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and the family of the house of Nathan by itself,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and their wives by themselves,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}and the family of the house of Levi by itself,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and their wives by themselves,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
the family of the Shimeites by itself,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and their wives by themselves,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}and all the families who are left, each by itself,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and their wives by themselves.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 13}On that day a fountain will be opened for the house of David,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and for the inhabitants of Jerusalem, for sin and for uncleanness.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}And it will be on that day, says the {\scaps Lord} of hosts,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I will cut off the names of the idols from the land and they will be remembered no more.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
And the prophets and the unclean spirit I will banish from the land.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}If any man prophesy any more,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
his father and his mother who bore him, will say to him,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8220*You will not live, for you speak falsehood in the name of the {\scaps Lord}.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
And his father and his mother who bore him will stab him through when he is seized by the prophetic frenzy.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}And it will be in that day that the prophets will be ashamed, each of his vision,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and will not wear the hairy mantle in order to deceive.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}Each will say, \uc1\u8220*I am not a prophet,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
