\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}And they will say to him, \uc1\u8220*What are these scars on your back?\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
And he will say, \uc1\u8220*The scars which I received in the house of my friends.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Awake, sword, against my shepherd,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
against the man who stands near to me,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
says the {\scaps Lord} of hosts.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I will strike the shepherd so that the sheep may be scattered,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
