\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and test it as one tests gold.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
Then they will call on my name,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
and I myself will answer them.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
I will say, \uc1\u8220*They are my people.\uc1\u8221*
\par}

